        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>KhumaloCraft is an online e-commerce store founded by James Khumalo where artists from around the world with different backgrounds and talents are allowed to upload their arts and crafts and sell them in support of their journey towards creative arts. We want to provide others within our community the opportunity to build a reputable brand for their talents. All profits go to the creator with KhumaloCraft only taking 10% of the sales. We strongly believe that art is a way of getting others to truly express a version of themselves hence we look forward to been on this journey with all the amazing artists around the world. </p>
